# Mind Measure Platform

**Canonical context:** [Platform handbook](https://docs.mindmeasure.co.uk/architecture/platform-handbook) (`mind-measure-docs/pages/architecture/platform-handbook.mdx`) — single source of truth for constraints, deploy workflow, session reading order, and repo list. If this rule file disagrees with the handbook, **update the handbook** and then align this file.

Mental health monitoring and support platform with two product lines: **University** (students) and **Pro** (corporate employees). All repos live under `/Users/keithduddy/Desktop/Mind Measure local /`.

