## Jodie Prompt Versions

Base prompt: `jodie_prompt_v2.md` in workspace root. Variants:
- `jodie_prompt_v2_uni.md` — student-facing (university context)
- `jodie_prompt_v2_pro.md` — employee-facing (workplace context)

Key rules: UK English, one question at a time, rotate acknowledgment phrases (never repeat), 6-8 exchanges before mood score, close with "Finish button".

